song.title: Tripping to Neptune
song.info: (c)basehead/klf 1994 composed in a few hours following a very bad hangover...! :) i hope ya like this one it's sort of ambient, sort of trance.. whateva. anyway, the samps are from a few places... roland 808 technomancer iv (cd) x-static goldmine (cd) don't techno vol.2 (cd) b.i.t. and Maelcum.. this one runs about 13:24 so sit back and chill.. quick greets to all irc guys and the klf crew. -bh! -7.16.94- -what'sinthebasket? mybrother!!-bh94!-
